Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:54.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Mommy? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:08.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:11.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] Dear Kureha, I'm going to\Nsend her back through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:14.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about us,\Nokay? We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:19.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is Mommy talking about?\NWhat door does she mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:31.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[sirens blaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:40.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA] You were the one who\Nfound and saved Kureha that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:44.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I cannot and will not allow\Nmy daughter's precious friend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,to be excluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:59.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Someday, I promise,\Nthe time will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:04.12,Main,,0,0,0,,when bears and people\Ncan be friends forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:09.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Take this pendant with you,\Nsweetie. It's a love charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:11.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I know it will help you\Nthe way it helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:13.59,Main,,0,0,0,,--[door closes]\N--[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] From the beginning,\Nwe hated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:42.54,Main,,0,0,0,,But also, we loved you from\Nthe beginning, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.75,Main,,0,0,0,,All we wanted was to become\Ntrue friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:49.13,Main,,0,0,0,,So we had to cross the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:54.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NYurikuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:56.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:47.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NDon't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That was, like, way too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you were a bear\Nand almost, like, shot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously, be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:58.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. Lulu thought she\Nwas, like, way busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing, growl,\Nno one said anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:05.31,Main,,0,0,0,,So, uh, what's with that truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:07.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a, like, way special\Nvehicle we just developed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,for bear annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NShock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuma shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NNasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:33.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NBuzz, buzz! Nasty, nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.04,Main,,0,0,0,,We cyborg-ized the\Ndead bear and are, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,using her to generate\Nelectricity, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:41.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're fighting fire with\Nfire! And bears with bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NEco-kumagical! Nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.47,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:49.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you come across\Nany bears around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Another one's, like,\Nbeen reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Apparently, someone near school\Nway saw a bear this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu hasn't seen anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:56.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Yeah, totally\Nreally! Not this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu hasn't seen one\Nsingle bear, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:04.41,Main,,0,0,0,,If you keep stupidly walking\Naround by yourself like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.12,Main,,0,0,0,,the bears are going\Nto eat you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:09.74,Main,,0,0,0,,You should try to be,\Nlike, way more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow. Talk about\Na close call, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:16.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway. Obviously,\Nit's not here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu wonders where to look next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL]\NHuh. I don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:24.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did Lulu Yurigasaki\Nbetray Ginko Yurishiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:26.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm bear shocked by\Nthe whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:29.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It's inconsistent.\NI thought what she wanted was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,for Ginko Yurishiro's love\Nto be returned to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Her actions are contradictory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE BEAUTY]\NYou are so dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.94,Main,,0,0,0,,It's because Ginko Yurishiro,\Nis loved by Lulu Yurigasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparkle, sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:44.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Love is varied, and comes\Nin more than one form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Love is special. Perhaps that's\Nwhy Kumaria questions everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.28,Main,,0,0,0,,who wants to go\Nbeyond Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:51.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Real love has the\Npower to endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:55.00,Main,,0,0,0,,The question stands,\N"Is your love the real thing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "Then, she laid\Ndown a ladder for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:03.21,Main,,0,0,0,,connecting the two worlds\Ntogether once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:04.67,Main,,0,0,0,,There they found a single,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:08.97,Main,,0,0,0,,vast mirror standing\Nlike a wall in their path.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Each girl saw her own\Nreflection in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.60,Main,,0,0,0,,They heard Kumaria's\Nvoice say..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NListen up! Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\N"Now, your friend is waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,just on the other side\Nof that very door."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] The Wall of Severance\Nhas, like, broken down...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "If you smash the\N'you' in the mirror to bits,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,if you tear yourself apart, she\Nshall grant you a Promise Kiss."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NTime for an exclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "But beware:\Nthis may cost you your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I will ask you one more time:\Nis your love the real thing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NI found it! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\N"The girls stared at themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.68,Main,,0,0,0,,in the mirror for\Na very long time."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:52.31,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the rest of Mom's book.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:55.18,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the future she\Nwanted to tell me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "The girls stared\Nat themselves in the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:02.36,Main,,0,0,0,,for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:05.28,Main,,0,0,0,,The moon girl summoned\Nall her courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:08.61,Main,,0,0,0,,'I want to cross the sky,\Nso I will smash that mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I will smash my image.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,The forest girl steeled\Nherself, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:17.29,Main,,0,0,0,,'I want to cross the sky, so\NI will destroy that mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:20.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I will tear my image to shreds.'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.50,Main,,0,0,0,,'My love is true!'"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:27.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "With that, the mirror\Nshattered in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.84,Main,,0,0,0,,And they each found their\Nfriend standing there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:32.97,Main,,0,0,0,,on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:37.06,Main,,0,0,0,,The two girls walked slowly\Nup to each other, and simply,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:41.90,Main,,0,0,0,,wordlessly, gave one another\Ntheir Promise Kisses."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:46.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "And so, having\Ncompleted their Promise Kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:49.15,Main,,0,0,0,,the two began a journey\Nbeyond severance,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:52.16,Main,,0,0,0,,guided by the star of love."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] This is our destiny?\NOur rightful future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko and I will go\Nbeyond severance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:05.46,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear and a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,That future isn't possible.\NThere's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.76,Main,,0,0,0,,--[door bell rings]\N--[KUREHA] Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:24.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NHold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my Mom's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NLulu came to give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.49,Main,,0,0,0,,But she should go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NNo, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:35.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NUh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Um. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:44.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You could, take a bath?\NY'know, before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:49.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NIs it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:52.17,Main,,0,0,0,,My mom used to wash my hair like\Nthis back when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I found out who was\Nbehind her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yuriika ate my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:02.14,Main,,0,0,0,,She was a bear disguised as\Na human, too. Like you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:04.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NBut now she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NMay I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:13.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] I know that Mitsuko\NYurizono was the one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:17.62,Main,,0,0,0,,who killed Sumika. So,\NI just, I can't figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.20,Main,,0,0,0,,why Ginko told me she\Nwas the one who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:21.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:25.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It's because Ginko thinks\Nit's her fault, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:26.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko did it,\Nbut Ginko still knew
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.30,Main,,0,0,0,,that Mitsuko was\Ngoing to eat Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:34.63,Main,,0,0,0,,And, she didn't save her.\NShe couldn't make herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:36.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.43,Main,,0,0,0,,She loves you with\Nall her heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.43,Main,,0,0,0,,so she wanted your\Nlove in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.31,Main,,0,0,0,,But with Sumika\Nstill in your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.98,Main,,0,0,0,,she wouldn't be able\Nto get that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko was jealous of Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,But Lulu is no better than her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:55.49,Main,,0,0,0,,because Lulu was a\Nsilly, jealous bear,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:58.45,Main,,0,0,0,,she betrayed Ginko,\Nand told on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:05.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko is why Sumika's dead.\NShe helped the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:10.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Lulu felt like you'd\Nstolen Ginko's love from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:13.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that crazy?\NAfter Lulu wished so long
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:15.97,Main,,0,0,0,,for you two to have\Nyour Promise Kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,she went and messed it all up.\NLulu's sorry. Big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:31.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, look at that. Guess Mom's\Npendant really was the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:36.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] See, that proves\Nyou were friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:42.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko won't lie to you,\Ngrowl. There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:46.58,Main,,0,0,0,,And you wanna know why? Because\Nyou are her precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:49.75,Main,,0,0,0,,She thinks I'm her\N"precious friend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,--[KUREHA laughs]\N--[GINKO] Growl. Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:58.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Were we...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:00.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you un-forget\Nsomething? Hope so!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:03.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] It's no good.\NI still can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:09.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, there is one thing\Nthat keeps coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:12.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I know for sure mom told\Nme Ginko was my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.02,Main,,0,0,0,,And when I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I sang the love song\Nwith a friend I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:19.11,Main,,0,0,0,,So that friend\Nmust've been Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,But now, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:23.78,Main,,0,0,0,,How could I simply forget\Nsomeone I cared about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:26.71,Main,,0,0,0,,None of this makes sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:31.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Why? Why are my only missing\Nmemories the ones of Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Something must have happened\Nbetween us. But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:41.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-pie, what's important\Nis Ginko loves you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:44.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, and now. Ginko doesn't\Nback down on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:48.64,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think you\Ncan forgive her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:51.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, growl. Can you try, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:57.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you try to be\Nher friend again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:12:59.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you please try\Nto love her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:03.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't. I'm sorry, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:04.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:10.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Humans and bears,\Nwe have severance between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,No one can overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NLulu guesses you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Lost love never comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, Kureha,\Nyou're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:31.44,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear has been,\Nlike, targeting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:35.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro and\NLulu Yurigasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:37.57,Main,,0,0,0,,They're really\Nbears in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.90,Main,,0,0,0,,We just found evidence\Nthat proves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:42.61,Main,,0,0,0,,One of them must be the bear\Nyou shot at on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.37,Main,,0,0,0,,The one you missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:46.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Which means you're,\Nlike, way in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:48.66,Main,,0,0,0,,She's bound to come\Nfor her revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:51.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Call us the second you\Nsense a bear nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll come take\Ncare of it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:53.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:56.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:59.84,Main,,0,0,0,,It's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:25.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[sirens blaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NI don't want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:32.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NHm? Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:44.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] They must've caught on.\NToo late. She won't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:47.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA, LULU panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. Kure-pie, why are\Nyou helping Lulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:52.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I just feel like this\Nis the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NUh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:03.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Search all corners of the\Nneighborhood, and set the trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:05.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NHey. Lulu just had an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:08.49,Main,,0,0,0,,She thinks she might know the\Nreason you lost your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:09.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Why you forgot Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:15.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] For a bear to become a\Ngirl, she has to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NA deal? With whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] With what stands\Nbetween humans and bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.21,Main,,0,0,0,,The Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:25.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NThe Wall. You mean those men?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The ones on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:30.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Yes. If they grant a\Nbear yuri approval in court,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.72,Main,,0,0,0,,she can become a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:35.64,Main,,0,0,0,,But to do that, you have\Nto let go of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.98,Main,,0,0,0,,It's usually whatever\Nyou care about the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Well, and this\Nis just Lulu's theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.86,Main,,0,0,0,,but Lulu bets in Ginkos's trial,\Nwhen they made her let go of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.70,Main,,0,0,0,,something, she had to\Nlet go of your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:51.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat? My love?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Right. She had to give\Nup on the love you gave her
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:56.37,Main,,0,0,0,,all those years ago. Lulu thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:59.92,Main,,0,0,0,,that's the reason Ginko\Ndisappeared from your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NThat's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:05.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU giggles] Lulu's so\Nclever. Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Lulu's pretty sure\Nyou can get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NGet what back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:11.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NYour love for Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:16.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Because you didn't\Nactually give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] At least that's\Nwhat Lulu believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:22.15,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, this really is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:25.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA pants, gasps]\NLulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NLulu Yurigasaki has revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:33.20,Main,,0,0,0,,the secret of transformation\Nto a third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:34.87,Main,,0,0,0,,For the offending bear,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:37.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approval is\Nterminated immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:40.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw! Can't we just\Ngive her a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:45.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not. Rules are\Nrules, and rules are cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lulu, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:53.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu's sorry, Kure-pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She wasn't supposed\Nto tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:01.65,Main,,0,0,0,,so now the court won't\Nlet her be a girl anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:08.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] We can't be\Ntogether ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGoodbye, Kure-pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:15.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmph. I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:31.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NFire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Firing, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:35.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NNasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:42.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NNasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:57.49,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not them.\NThis bear is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NWhat? Kure-pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] I won't do it. I'll\Nnever let a friend be excluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:20.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[sirens blaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:35.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello? Who's out\Nthere calling to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:43.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "There is one way\Nto make your wish come true."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "In the center\Nof the sky is a place
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:51.17,Main,,0,0,0,,called the Door to Friendship."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:57.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\N"If your love is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:19:00.10,Main,,0,0,0,,your friend will be\Nwaiting for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:21.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "You'll find her on\Nthe other side of that door."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA panting] That's it!\NThe Door to Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Just like the picture\NI saw in Mom's book!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:33.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I met Ginko on the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NKure-pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It is! I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:44.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Hello? I think I heard\Nsomeone out here calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:55.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:59.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:09.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Are you the one\Nwho's been calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You and\NI can be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,So you don't have\Nto be alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,This is it. This is\Nwhere it all began.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:40.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] That day, I crossed the\NWall of Severance and met Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:45.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I remember, now. Ginko,\Nyou really were my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:48.62,Main,,0,0,0,,And I... I do love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:55.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] You can get to\Nthe other side of the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:59.17,Main,,0,0,0,,through here, Lulu. You can go\Nsafely back to the bear world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:02.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-pie. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:06.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Please tell Lulu she finally\Nmanaged to become your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:12.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but, no, you are\Nstill not my friend, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:21.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you, I will never\Nforgive the bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,If I see you again,\NI'll shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot straight,\Nand I know I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NGo. Get out of here, now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:33.96,Main,,0,0,0,,and don't you ever\Ncome back, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:38.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You belong over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:05.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Goodbye. I had to\Ndo the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:12.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] I knew the evil\Nwould end up being you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\N♪ Yuri ga aku. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:16.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:19.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Who knew this door would be a,\Nlike, way secret passage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:21.22,Main,,0,0,0,,through the Wall of Severance?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:25.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] You're the traitor who\Nbrought bears into our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You joined the bears,\Nadmit it! All this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:30.77,Main,,0,0,0,,you've been taking revenge\Non us for excluding you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:32.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true! [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kureha Tsubaki.\NIt's all over, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:40.48,Main,,0,0,0,,And you're gonna, like, pay for\Ntaking our friends' lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:44.53,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! The hunt's\Njust getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:49.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NI found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:51.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:53.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.34,0:24:29.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NLet the Yuri Trial, begin.
